name: Floki CEO Coin
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is Floki CEO Coin?

Launched in 24/02/2023 by a team based in United States of America, Floki CEO Coin is a meme cryptocurrency token built on Binance Smart Chain with a 5% of each transaction being rewarded to the holders. Floki CEO's main goal is to release its own play to earn game with Floki as its main character and with upgradable NFTs. These features are developed under FCC ecosystem. Floki CEO Coin is available on P2B Centralized Exchange and also on PancakeSwap Decentralized Exchange.
